{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
'''Mselliet''' is an area in the northern [[Malta]]. Most of it is made up of [[agriculture|agricultural land]]. The area is also home for two [[private school]]s [[San Anton School]] and [[San Andrea School]].

